summary: Have I been spending the entire day brainstorming sticker ideas?  Maybe. In the bottom I’ve got 12 Kingdom’s Taiki, an alt-color...
caption:
Have I been spending the entire day brainstorming sticker ideas?  Maybe.

In the bottom I’ve got 12 Kingdom’s Taiki, an alt-color for my Kirin sticker, then an Ace Unicorn (needs more plurple), and an aro Pegasus!  I may end up doing a kickstarter for these stickers, if there’s enough interest.  (Or if I get a good enough job that I can foot some fancy printing.)

summary: “And thank you for stopping by!” “May I have a moment of your time, please?” Greetings, fellow stranger! Tis I, another...
body:
“And thank you for stopping by!”
“May I have a moment of your time, please?”

Greetings, fellow stranger!
Tis I, another stranger, who also happens to draw things and stuff.
Could I interest you in some of my fine wares?
I’d love to finally get this little business started and every little bit counts!
Long story short:

I will NOT draw anything underage, pedographic, pedopornographic and such.
Anything else can be discussed privately.

In case you aren’t buying just yet, or at all, may I ask you to please reblog this post?
I’d mean the world for me.
Thank you!
